title: Marble Muse-HI2U
description:
HI2U!
     
    Marble Muse (c) Ketos Games
     
    Release Date : 16/08/2015
    Protection   : Steam
    Type         : Casual, Indie, Simulation
    Size         : 1 Disc
     
    Description:
    ~~~~~~~~~~~~
     
    Marble Muse is an indie physics based game, where you tilt the environment
    using gravity to navigate a marble through increasingly mind bending courses.
    Enter the inventor's workshop with many elaborate levels to master and many
    hidden secrets to discover. Test all his inventions, starting with proof of
    concept and ending with the finished product.
     
     
    Features
    * 24 levels
    * Levels made of cardboard, wood, metal, electronic components, etc.
    * Bronze, Silver, Gold and Platinum(Challenge mode) times to beat.
    * Secrets mode for each level - Find the hidden marble and red stars.
    * Challenge mode for each level - The marble moves twice as fast.
    * Marble selection
    * Steam Achievements
     
     
    Install:
    ~~~~~~~
    Unrar, mount/burn, install the game, copy crack and play!
